      "text": "Hash functions are one way deterministic functions.\nOne-way -> Once encrypted can never be decrypted\nDeterministic -> Given the same input it will always generate the same output",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hash functions are one way deterministic functions.\nOne-way -> Once encrypted can never be decrypted\nDeterministic -> Given the same input it will always generate the same output",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
